**/.dockerignore
````````
# Git and version control
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# IDE and editors
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.toolstarget

# User-specific files
**/*.*proj.user
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/*.suo
**/*.user

# Build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/out
**/publish

# Docker files
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/.dockerignore

# Node modules
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log

# Kubernetes configs (not needed in image)
**/k8s/
**/*.yaml
**/*.yml
!**/appsettings*.json

# Documentation
*.md
README.md
LICENSE

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/*.trx

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Temporary files
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/.tmp/
**/azds.yaml
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml

# ============================================
# EXCLUDE WPF PROJECT (desktop app, not for Docker)
# ============================================
SteelDesignerEngineer.WPF/
**/SteelDesignerEngineer.WPF/**

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/.env